# OlsFunctional.lean

Purely functional model of the OLS linear regression estimator, as
would be generated by the Aeneas toolchain when translating
`scientific_compute::discovery::linear_regression` from Rust MIR to Lean 4.

## Translation pipeline

```
scientific_compute/src/discovery.rs
    │
    │  rustc --emit=mir
    ▼
target/debug/deps/scientific_compute-<hash>.mir
    │
    │  aeneas --backend lean
    ▼
lean4/OlsFunctional.lean   ← this file
    │
